Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Decision Utility Module Stub
Provides comprehensive utility theory with multi-attribute utility and prospect theory
Enables utility optimization, preference learning, and decision elicitation methods
:End Note

Type UtilityFunction is Dictionary with:
    function_id as String
    function_type as String
    function_parameters as Dictionary
    function_bounds as List[Float]
    function_properties as Dictionary

Type MultiAttributeUtility is Dictionary with:
    mau_id as String
    attributes as List[Attribute]
    value_functions as List[ValueFunction]
    aggregation_method as String
    attribute_weights as List[Float]
    mau_properties as Dictionary

Type Attribute is Dictionary with:
    attribute_id as String
    attribute_name as String
    attribute_type as String
    attribute_bounds as List[Float]
    attribute_preference as String
    attribute_metadata as Dictionary

Type ValueFunction is Dictionary with:
    function_id as String
    attribute_ref as String
    function_type as String
    function_parameters as Dictionary
    function_bounds as List[Float]
    function_metadata as Dictionary

Type ProspectTheoryModel is Dictionary with:
    model_id as String
    value_function as UtilityFunction
    probability_weighting as ProbabilityWeighting
    reference_point as Float
    model_parameters as Dictionary
    model_properties as Dictionary

Type ProbabilityWeighting is Dictionary with:
    weighting_id as String
    weighting_type as String
    weighting_parameters as Dictionary
    weighting_function as String
    weighting_metadata as Dictionary

Type UtilityOptimizer is Dictionary with:
    optimizer_id as String
    optimization_method as String
    optimization_parameters as Dictionary
    convergence_criteria as Dictionary
    optimizer_properties as Dictionary

Type PreferenceData is Dictionary with:
    data_id as String
    preference_pairs as List[Dictionary]
    preference_strengths as List[Float]
    preference_metadata as Dictionary

Type UtilitySystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    utility_functions as List[UtilityFunction]
    optimization_engines as List[OptimizationEngine]
    elicitation_methods as List[ElicitationMethod]
    system_configuration as Dictionary
    system_metadata as Dictionary

Process called "create_utility_function" that takes config as Dictionary returns UtilityFunction
Process called "evaluate_utility" that takes utility_function as UtilityFunction and outcome as Float returns Float
Process called "evaluate_piecewise_utility" that takes utility_function as UtilityFunction and outcome as Float returns Float
Process called "calculate_expected_utility" that takes utility_function as UtilityFunction and lottery as Dictionary returns Float
Process called "find_certainty_equivalent" that takes utility_function as UtilityFunction and lottery as Dictionary returns Float
Process called "find_utility_inverse" that takes utility_function as UtilityFunction and target_utility as Float returns Float
Process called "create_multi_attribute_utility" that takes config as Dictionary returns MultiAttributeUtility
Process called "create_attribute" that takes config as Dictionary returns Attribute
Process called "create_value_function" that takes attribute as Attribute and config as Dictionary returns ValueFunction
Process called "evaluate_multi_attribute_utility" that takes mau as MultiAttributeUtility and alternative as Dictionary returns Float
Process called "evaluate_additive_utility" that takes mau as MultiAttributeUtility and alternative as Dictionary returns Float
Process called "evaluate_multiplicative_utility" that takes mau as MultiAttributeUtility and alternative as Dictionary returns Float
Process called "create_prospect_theory_model" that takes config as Dictionary returns ProspectTheoryModel
Process called "create_prospect_value_function" that takes config as Dictionary returns UtilityFunction
Process called "evaluate_prospect_value" that takes model as ProspectTheoryModel and outcome as Float returns Float
Process called "create_probability_weighting" that takes config as Dictionary returns ProbabilityWeighting
Process called "calculate_decision_weight" that takes weighting as ProbabilityWeighting and probability as Float returns Float
Process called "create_utility_optimizer" that takes config as Dictionary returns UtilityOptimizer
Process called "optimize_utility" that takes optimizer as UtilityOptimizer and decision_variables as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "solve_gradient_ascent" that takes optimizer as UtilityOptimizer and initial_point as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "learn_utility_from_preferences" that takes preference_data as List[Dictionary] and config as Dictionary returns UtilityFunction
Process called "learn_utility_maximum_likelihood" that takes preference_data as List[Dictionary] and function_form as String returns UtilityFunction
Process called "elicit_utility_function" that takes config as Dictionary returns UtilityFunction
Process called "elicit_by_certainty_equivalent" that takes attribute_range as List[Float] and config as Dictionary returns UtilityFunction
Process called "create_utility_system" that takes configuration as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_utility_optimization" that takes system as Dictionary and query as Dictionary returns Dictionary 